{"tid":2202951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（國際反應觀察）閆麗夢報告咁少關注原因 似乎因為佢同班農行太近","createTime":"2020-09-15T03:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T14:07:44.000Z","uid":66087,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c29e7969ed9744611171af3d24d4fb183422c4a9","tid":2202951,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:59:42.000Z","msg":"首先，班農最近名聲好差，有2個原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1，因為佢詐騙比人拉左<br />\n<br />\n（想追番件事嘅朋友自己睇）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200821/M5GB4HWSIFBLFMBBBMQHXS6Q6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200821%2FM5GB4HWSIFBLFMBBBMQHXS6Q6I%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhaccVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=4e2a51cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200821%2FM5GB4HWSIFBLFMBBBMQHXS6Q6I%2F&h=c8049582\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200821/M5GB4HWSIFBLFMBBBMQHXS6Q6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2，佢個 Youtube channel 陰謀論太多，令普通美國人覺得煩厭。"},{"pid":"a4c5f8078e098a2297f9b232be82e7536d851afd","tid":2202951,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:02:21.000Z","msg":"因為缺乏直接證據，隻病毒之前都俾好多人研究過，暫時都冇乜新發現。"},{"pid":"87f8dfbe6a5b9ef099e2744d6ca81141915272f0","tid":2202951,"uid":294518,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"#閆麗夢 博士關於冠狀病毒起源的論文發佈後，在12小時內，總瀏覽量和總下載量已經排到了著名的學術分享網站Zenodo歷史上所有八十萬篇論文的第3位， 不重復下載量（unique download）排在第2位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對，您沒看錯，確實是所有八十萬篇論文的第3位，而且僅用了12小時<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7MmBvu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7MmBvu.png&h=708c7be3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a651cffd2510e88ca5ae5408e2f725c7a252f0af","tid":2202951,"uid":66087,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"所以依家個情況好似「狼來了」<br />\n<br />\n因為Banon個 channel陰謀論太多，跟住又因為詐騙比人拉左，導致普遍美國人非常唔信 Banon<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏閻麗夢因為班農出名<br />\n<br />\n所以，依家唯一辦法係同Banon大割，先可以令份報告有人信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc18ea1bd026cdd61d9f7cab9412a15291139d9","tid":2202951,"uid":2656,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩出無耐, 其他國家啲科學家唔洗face check咩...<br />\n你估好似連登仔日日炒車咁唔怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90ab24f16a8c6422c5a41a6b0e00fb0da25a784","tid":2202951,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c6a5c6c6747c5328cc68c82c3e64818b906258a","tid":2202951,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afc18ea1bd026cdd61d9f7cab9412a15291139d9","tid":2202951,"uid":2656,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩出無耐, 其他國家啲科學家唔洗face check咩...<br />\n你估好似連登仔日日炒車咁唔怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"你起下樓主底先啦<br />\n根本成堆科學家都未驗證完係咪vaild<br />\n就話無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8718afa21502970c7076de0ec0c78272fe2b707","tid":2202951,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"afc18ea1bd026cdd61d9f7cab9412a15291139d9","tid":2202951,"uid":2656,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩出無耐, 其他國家啲科學家唔洗face check咩...<br />\n你估好似連登仔日日炒車咁唔怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T04:40:52.000Z","msg":"連登眾車手從來唔怕炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8259b49f82f234421c62b5a6587b2b2c0bdb7291","tid":2202951,"uid":328494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"呢啲基因研究嘢太專業，一般人連入門級都唔會明，<br />\n就算係生物學家或者醫學家之類，如果唔係嗰個範疇都唔會明。<br />\n你估好似啲社評人9up幾句咁易？"},{"pid":"f2058cdcc8bf3b6d8fa